# The Education of Women in Togo, Africa

This repository is a reference for research in women's education. We used [countries' unemployment rates](https://www.ilo.org/shinyapps/bulkexplorer17/?lang=en&segment=indicator&id=SDG_0852_SEX_AGE_RT_A&ref_&sex=SEX_T+SEX_M+SEX_F+SEX_O&classif1=AGE_YTHADULT_YGE15+AGE_YTHADULT_Y15-64+AGE_YTHADULT_Y15-24+AGE_YTHADULT_YGE25&timefrom=2000&timeto=2020), [countries' wages](https://www.ilo.org/shinyapps/bulkexplorer39/?lang=en&segment=indicator&id=EAR_4MMN_CUR_NB_A&ref_&classif1=CUR_TYPE_LCU+CUR_TYPE_PPP+CUR_TYPE_USD&timefrom=2000&timeto=2020), and [years of education of women by country](https://databank.worldbank.org/Years-of-Schooling-(Female)/id/c92e7408) datasets in our analyses. Running data through this code produces various statistical test results and graphs to go along with them. All datasets cover the years from 2000-2020.

Please consult researchers for more information.
